---
title: Sunny California Pork Salad with Guacamole Dressing
description: Everything you love about a California Pork sammie but in salad form! Chalk full of juicy tomatoes, crisp lettuce,  zesty spiced meat, sharp cheddar and drizzled with a guacamole dressing!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sunny-california-pork-salad-de8fdfec-0c96fb8c.jpg
